<div class="title">Willing to Tell My Darkest Secrets?</div>
<div class="substance">Midazolam</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Loralei&Exact=1">Loralei</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Loralei. "Willing to Tell My Darkest Secrets?: An Experience with Midazolam (exp43607)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jul 23, 2007. erowid.org/exp/43607</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
<tr><td></td><td width="15">&nbsp;</td></tr>
</table>

